						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Parakēśarivarman <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Rājēndra-Chōḻadēva I, Year 19 = 1031 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Gift of 30 cows for a lamp. The temple is called Tiruvīraṭṭānamuḍaiya-Mahādēvar in Tiruttaṇiyal, in Kuṉṟvarttanakōṭṭam. The donor Nandi Nandiy-ēṟn <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Taṇiyal Muttaraiyaṉ, a <hi rend="italic">paḷḷi</hi> of the village.</p>						

